===Etymology===
From Greek.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|system|systems}}

# A [[collection]] of [[organized]] things; as, a [[solar system]].
# A [[way]] of [[organising]] or [[planning]].
# A [[whole]] [[composed]] of [[relationship]]s among the [[member]]s.

